            <description><![CDATA[【女子耳朵被脓堵死！医生：有人掏耳朵掏成癌<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】小彩（化名）是采耳馆里的资深常客，平常更是习惯给自己掏耳朵，这天掏完耳朵后，小彩的耳朵竟出血了，虽然止了血，但吃饭时，小彩连嘴都没办法张开，右半边脸也肿了起来，甚至听人说话也费劲！小彩老公看了，马上将她送到了医院。医生用耳镜仔细看了看小彩的耳道，全明白了：耳道内出现充血、肿胀，最可怕的是，里面的脓跟流出来的血液已经混在一起，把耳道口堵死了👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫科普故事汇#</span></a> <a href="https://weibo.cn/sinaurl?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FcOeUyoHLyQ4NoOFkimdUOw" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hc2zk7qshfj20qy7ps1kx.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hc2zk60au3j20th7ps1kx.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hc2zk8ep6tj20u03l4n6k.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hc2zkuhyldg20dn07qawo.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
